    <stitle>ELECTRICAL SYSTEM TROUBLESHOOTING GUIDE - 5000i and 9000i - CAB ACCESSORIES - OPERATION - ELECTRIC HORN
    </stitle>
    <svcman/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="operate" graphiccount="0">
        <title>ELECTRIC HORN</title>
        <para>Battery power from 15A fuse F5-C is always available to the horn relay (463)/R7 at the common terminal
            (30) and control coil (86). Depressing the horn closes the relay ground circuit energizing the relay and
            applying power to the horn.
        </para>
    </svcproc>
